# Versioning and contracts

- No explicit versioning scheme in-repo (static frontend). Cache-bust query params (?v=...) are not generated by a build in-repo; clarify with tech lead how to update them. See ./docs/06-versioning-and-evolution.md.
- When changing _parametrs_new or _parametrs: recompile all entry SCSS that import them and verify landing, company, and search. When renaming classes/IDs used by HTML or JS, update all references. See ./docs/06-versioning-and-evolution.md.
- Do not change the linkMore contract (page, child-type, data-recipient, GET /{childType}?page=N, fragment response) without updating both frontend and backend. Do not change paywall wrapper/overlay/popup structure without aligning all pages and shared SCSS.
- For substantial architectural or contract changes, update ./docs and .cursor/rules per .cursor/rules/00-rules-generator.mdc.
